DigitalGov,Search,formerly,USASearch,is,a,service,provided,by,the,U,S,General,Services,Administration,GSA,It,hosts,the,Jobs,API,which,allows,users,to,access,a,list,of,current,job,openings,with,federal,state,and,local,government,agencies,Jobs,are,searchable,by,keyword,location,agency,schedule,or,any,combination,thereof,The,API,operates,via,REST,calls,issued,in,JSON,format